               <div class="ds-1col node node-idea-story node-teaser view-mode-teaser"> 
                <h2 class="insights-label insights">Insights</h2> 
                <div class="field field-name-field-image-key-image field-type-image field-label-hidden">
                 <img src="http://www.gsb.stanford.edu/sites/gsb/files/photo-men-skateboard-bike.jpg" width="1630" height="955" alt="Young guys on skateboards and an older man on a bike">
                </div>
                <div class="field-group-format group_wrapper_idea_story_text field-group-div group-wrapper-idea-story-text  speed-none effect-none">
                 <div class="field field-name-field-date field-type-datetime field-label-hidden">
                  <span class="date-display-single">February 11, 2015</span>
                 </div>
                 <span class="media-icon Written"><span class="element-invisible">Written</span></span>
                 <span class="field field-name-title field-type-ds field-label-hidden"><h2><a href="/insights/six-reasons-rethink-aging-retirement">Six Reasons to Rethink Aging and Retirement</a></h2></span>
                 <div class="field field-name-field-editorial-summary field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
                  Researchers at the Stanford Center on Longevity explain that what we think about mental health, exercise, and financial stability is wrong.
                 </div>
                 <div class="field field-name-field-key-taxonomy field-type-entityreference field-label-hidden">
